{"tid":1228701,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解潘曉穎條命就係命，太古義士條命就賤過袋底泥？","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T01:28:33.000Z","uid":104555,"like":154,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ec6a647953b34d6dfb1f432b547b88d2cbe8f9","tid":1228701,"uid":104555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:46:46.000Z","msg":"潘小姐遇害實屬不幸，但講到底佢只係一隻淫亂、派綠帽既<span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞</span>。<br />\n因為佢同陳同佳既私怨，危害香港法治、自由，要接受中國<span style=\"color: red;\">人治、獨裁管治、黨治</span>既法律體系引渡，令國安局特工和維穩部門可以<span style=\"color: red;\">明正言順虜劫異見人士或外資龍頭</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林奠口口聲聲話要幫潘氏沉冤，但硬推修正案加劇民怨，撕裂社會，義士傷亡入獄者不計其數。<span style=\"color: red;\">潘小姐條命就貴，我地條命就賤撚到貼地</span>。矛盾之處罄竹難書：<br />\n1. 為潘曉穎沉冤，彰顯公義<br />\n-台灣當局卻一早表明拒絕接收修正案下移交的逃犯，惟特首置之不顧，為中國進一步掌控香港而硬<br />\n推法案，<span style=\"color: red;\">消費死者，死後都要做政治condom</span>。<br />\n2. 不想香港成為「犯罪天堂」<br />\n-可是政府在修正兩次後，篩選剩下三十餘項七年以上的嚴重控罪，<span style=\"color: red;\">並不涵蓋商業罪案等</span>，以此討好商界。<span style=\"color: red;\">篩選過既「公義」，還算是公義？放過七年以下既逃犯，卻可以免淪為逃犯天堂？</span><br />\n3. 加強人權保障<br />\n國內人權狀況大家都知咩料，上訴法官竟然係原審法官、法官係效忠於黨而非自身公正性、好多時連辯護律師都係控方既針，<span style=\"color: red;\">偏偏賊婆意氣風發、不可一世，要令香港人、投資者活在陰影之下，仲以為自己好正義好岩</span><br />\n<br />\n林奠將香港硬實力上賣入「大媽區」、將香港大半百年積蓄耗於「明日大愚」及以逃犯條例嚇走外資<br />\n軟實力上，斷送香港法治、司法獨立及特區地位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以未訓既巴打絲打，好希望大家認真諗清楚，因為要死既唔係我地，呢個淪陷既政府唔值得我地犧牲<br />\n<br />\n6. 16!</span>"},{"pid":"886d865c3f99b0b3afee424d926cde92b18a6ad1","tid":1228701,"uid":232594,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"屌手滑撳撚左負評<br />\n我係要比正評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92e16a80e8346f605f8b282ad3463f14f115700","tid":1228701,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886d865c3f99b0b3afee424d926cde92b18a6ad1","tid":1228701,"uid":232594,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"屌手滑撳撚左負評<br />\n我係要比正評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"巴打聽日會唔會見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7af4a2c5361abc8c77c39c287c4ca778503e743","tid":1228701,"uid":2156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f9c1f14a1b3084a4293e2030001f99ebd992fb1d","tid":1228701,"uid":232594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c92e16a80e8346f605f8b282ad3463f14f115700","tid":1228701,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886d865c3f99b0b3afee424d926cde92b18a6ad1","tid":1228701,"uid":232594,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"屌手滑撳撚左負評<br />\n我係要比正評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n